{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 61,
  "title": "第六十一章（處下）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "大邦者，下流也。天下之牝，天下之交也。"
    },
    {
      "text": "牝恆以靚勝牡。為亓靚也，故宜為下。"
    },
    {
      "text": "大邦以下小邦，則取小邦。小邦以下大邦，則取於大邦。故：或下以取。或下而取。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故：大邦者，不過欲兼畜人。小邦者，不過欲入事人。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫皆得亓欲，則大者宜為下。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 19,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "治大國，當如居下流，不逆細微。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大國，天下士民之所交會。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "牝者，陰類也。柔謙和而不昌也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "陰道以安靜為謙下。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 37,
          "end": 37
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "能謙下之，則常有之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 37,
          "end": 37
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "此言國無大小，能持謙畜人，則無過失也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 27,
          "end": 28
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "下者謂大國以下小國，小國以下大國，更以義相取。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 37,
          "end": 37
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大國不失下，則兼併小國而牧畜之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 37,
          "end": 37
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "使為臣僕。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大國小國各欲得其所，大國又宜為謙下。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 19,
          "end": 19
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "江海居大而處下，則百川流之，大國居大而處下，則天下流之，故曰，大國下流也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 14,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天下所歸會也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 9,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "靜而不求，物自歸之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 17,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以其靜故能為下也。牝，雌也。雄躁動貪欲，雌常以靜，故能勝雄也。以其靜復能為下，故物歸之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 37,
          "end": 37
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大國以下，猶云以大國下小國。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 37,
          "end": 37
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "小國則附之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 37,
          "end": 37
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大國納之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 27,
          "end": 28
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言唯修卑下，然後乃各得其所。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "小國修下自全而已，不能令天下歸之，大國修下則天下歸之。故曰，各得其所欲，則大者宜為下也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
